Package it.polimi.travlendarplus.RESTful

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpResponseBuilder
    This class provide a set of static methods that are used to build all the HTTP responses sent by Travlendar+ application server
    TravlendarRESTful
    Defines the base URI for all resource URIs.
    TripRESTful
    This class provide all RESTful methods related to handle the users trips This RESTful resource will be hosted at the relative URI path "/trip"
